column5: Hi all!! I've never fished Lac Suel as I usually go fish around LOTW and Kenora. I'm wondering if there are any campgrounds near (less than 5 miles) Lac Suel and a boat landing. If so, do I have to purchase a permit to camp, or can you pay when you show up?? Are they usually full in the summer??? Thanks for the help. upnorth8
www.goldpines.com had great fishing out of here last year best ever
